title: Ukrainian beehive Bjilnyk
text: Brood chambers can be made either 8 or 10 standard Langstroth or Dadant frame different height, as well as supers by 17 or 21 of these frames or frame smaller height (medium, shallow or half-frame Dadant type). Thickness of wall board is 20 mm. You should pay attention to the size of the boxes (meter or inch standard and 8 or 10 frames).
